Dear members of the netmeta community,

I am conducting a network meta-analysis and have been using a log-response
ratio as the effect size estimator. For each pairwise treatment comparison
in each study,we calculate the ratio as:
[image: Inline image 2]

where Ybar1 and Ybar2 are the means for each of the treatments reported in
